## DESCRIPTION
## A buoy is swinging on lang, find the natural period of the system.
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## KEYWORDS('buoy', 'Energy Methods','Natural Period')
## DBsubject(Dynamics)
## DBchapter(Vibration)
## DBsection(Energy Methods)
## Date(2020-06-23)
## Author(Daniel Youm)
## Institution(University of British Columbia)
## Level(Intermediate)
